item.title: I really wana make my own server on a no-ip but i dont know how to
item.dc:creator: @Red_Wave Red Wave
item.description:
@Red_Wave wrote:

go to no-ip.com first, then register. once u done that go to “add” and add ur server name and ip, (port whatever u want) leave the rest the same then hit “create”.
then go to downloads at the top then download (windows if u have windows. linux if u have linux etc.) then click next through all of it then at the end itll say login type ur email, and password u registered with, then it should have ur server ip with a box beside it, check it then ur done!
